# ============================================
# SUPABASE DATABASE CONNECTION INSTRUCTIONS
# ============================================

# 1. Go to: https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/zolidmgttqkmmxourdpd/settings/database

# 2. Look for "Connection string" section

# 3. Select "URI" tab (not "Transaction" or "Session")

# 4. Copy the connection string that looks like:
#    postgresql://postgres.zolidmgttqkmmxourdpd:[YOUR-PASSWORD]@aws-0-us-east-1.pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres

# 5. Replace [YOUR-PASSWORD] with your actual database password

# 6. Update the DATABASE_URL in Backend/.env with this connection string

# EXAMPLE (replace with your actual password):
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres.zolidmgttqkmmxourdpd:YOUR_ACTUAL_PASSWORD@aws-0-us-east-1.pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres

